like earlier happens,

69
00:06:56,669 --> 00:06:59,469
it means I agree not to ask

70
00:06:59,639 --> 00:07:01,639
for a resuscitation.

71
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:05,809
I signed that three times already.

72
00:07:08,049 --> 00:07:10,279
First, when he was
admitted to the hospital.

73
00:07:12,119 --> 00:07:15,119
Second, around this time last year.

74
00:07:17,119 --> 00:07:18,619
And today.

75
00:07:23,189 --> 00:07:24,959
I signed it just now.

76
00:07:29,829 --> 00:07:31,329
When I came,

77
00:07:32,899 --> 00:07:34,569
like my mom said,

78
00:07:35,969 --> 00:07:38,179
I steeled myself.

79
00:07:41,749 --> 00:07:43,149
If that happened

80
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:50,519
while I'm not there,

81
00:07:52,219 --> 00:07:53,459
then

82
00:07:54,619 --> 00:07:56,829
I'd ask them to do

83
00:07:57,689 --> 00:07:59,849
what it says on the form.

84
00:08:03,329 --> 00:08:05,359
But he's right before my eyes.

85
00:08:06,339 --> 00:08:07,839
He's right before me.

86
00:08:09,209 --> 00:08:11,469
So I have to beg them to save him.

87
00:08:48,809 --> 00:08:51,209
For people who come now and then,

88
00:08:51,519 --> 00:08:53,919
it seems he's just
lying in bed, sleeping.

89
00:08:55,319 --> 00:08:57,119
But if you see him every day,

90
00:08:57,349 --> 00:08:59,289
if you're with him every day,

91
00:09:02,089 --> 00:09:04,799
every moment is different.

92
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:07,629
He smiles when something's funny.

93
00:09:08,769 --> 00:09:10,369
He cries when he's sad.

94
00:09:13,499 --> 00:09:15,939
The last few days, he smiled a lot.

95
00:09:23,209 --> 00:09:25,449
So I asked them to
resuscitate him again.

96
00:09:31,989 --> 00:09:33,359
Jeong-su.

97
00:09:34,789 --> 00:09:36,829
What should I tell my mom?

98
00:10:39,319 --> 00:10:40,719
What time is it?

99
00:10:45,429 --> 00:10:46,959
Past ten, right?

100
00:10:49,099 --> 00:10:50,099
Yes.

101
00:10:59,809 --> 00:11:01,309
I have to be on the set at four.

102
00:11:01,309 --> 00:11:03,279
But I can't sleep at home.

103
00:11:08,989 --> 00:11:10,149
Sit.

104
00:11:11,489 --> 00:11:13,159
Is it busy outside?

105
00:11:14,159 --> 00:11:15,189
No.

106
00:11:17,859 --> 00:11:19,129
Things are going slow.

107
00:11:24,299 --> 00:11:25,499
Are you

108
00:11:25,669 --> 00:11:27,169
seeing someone nowadays?

109
00:11:28,609 --> 00:11:29,709
Me?

110
00:11:31,479 --> 00:11:32,539
No.

111
00:11:34,579 --> 00:11:35,579
Okay.

112
00:11:37,849 --> 00:11:38,849
Why?

113
00:11:39,279 --> 00:11:40,279
Nothing.

114
00:11:41,219 --> 00:11:44,719
You just have a different vibe.

115
00:11:47,459 --> 00:11:49,429
Except for paying more taxes,

116
00:11:49,429 --> 00:11:50,829
nothing has changed with me.

117
00:11:53,759 --> 00:11:56,369
Your comments smell of money now.

118
00:11:58,469 --> 00:11:59,839
Be careful.

119
00:11:59,999 --> 00:12:03,439
If you suddenly become rich,
people start hating.

120
00:12:04,409 --> 00:12:05,809
I'll be careful.

121
00:12:16,919 --> 00:12:17,919
You know

122
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:20,439
the account last time.

123
00:12:23,529 --> 00:12:25,729
The one that posted the story about

124
00:12:26,959 --> 00:12:30,369
my secret kid on
my 10th wedding anniversary.

125
00:12:32,369 --> 00:12:33,539
That account

126
00:12:34,469 --> 00:12:35,809
disappeared.

127
00:12:36,509 --> 00:12:37,439
Oh.

128
00:12:38,409 --> 00:12:39,279
Yes.

129
00:12:40,839 --> 00:12:42,149
Did you remove it?

130
00:12:43,909 --> 00:12:44,879
Yes.

131
00:12:45,949 --> 00:12:47,519
You don't know who it is?

132
00:12:48,819 --> 00:12:50,619
All I did was remove it.

133
00:12:51,919 --> 00:12:53,459
So I don't know who it is.

134
00:12:55,959 --> 00:12:56,959
Okay.

135
00:12:58,959 --> 00:13:01,129
I can't report it because it's true.

136
00:13:07,769 --> 00:13:09,239
Was it you?

137
00:13:21,149 --> 00:13:22,719
The only people who know about it

138
00:13:23,789 --> 00:13:25,189
are you, me,

139
00:13:25,959 --> 00:13:27,359
Mr. Seo

140
00:13:28,789 --> 00:13:30,829
and Writer Lee.

141
00:13:32,999 --> 00:13:34,759
It can't be Mr. Seo.

142
00:13:35,629 --> 00:13:38,129
Even though he's out of control,

143
00:13:38,799 --> 00:13:39,999
he's his father.

144
00:13:51,179 --> 00:13:52,649
It wasn't me.

145
00:13:58,819 --> 00:14:00,189
Then it was her.

146
00:14:10,729 --> 00:14:13,239
I wonder what will be
posted the next morning.

147
00:14:14,439 --> 00:14:16,269
There might be a post saying

148
00:14:17,109 --> 00:14:19,639
"woke" Jeong Ah-ran
has a kid in Canada who

149
00:14:19,639 --> 00:14:22,309
hasn't seen his mother in 20 years.

150
00:14:23,049 --> 00:14:24,379
That's absurd.

151
00:14:26,319 --> 00:14:28,649
I'm scared to even look up my name.

152
00:14:30,319 --> 00:14:32,189
So this is "shield lift."

153
00:14:32,989 --> 00:14:35,459
Your closest person
stabbing you in the back.

154
00:14:38,929 --> 00:14:40,629
Don't Google your name.

155
00:14:42,999 --> 00:14:44,399
You just get upset.

156
00:14:45,199 --> 00:14:46,929
There are good posts, too.

157
00:14:47,069 --> 00:14:49,709
I just don't know
if they mean it or not.

158
00:14:50,539 --> 00:14:51,609
How can I not look?

159
00:14:51,609 --> 00:14:53,109
I'm curious to death.

160
00:14:54,739 --> 00:14:56,739
What are you so curious about?

161
00:14:58,679 --> 00:15:01,279
About what people think about me.

162
00:15:03,549 --> 00:15:05,119
When I find a nasty comment,

163
00:15:06,019 --> 00:15:08,859
I go to their friend's
friend account and look.

164
00:15:09,089 --> 00:15:10,229
To see what kind of person they are,

165
00:15:10,229 --> 00:15:12,899
what they eat, how they live...

166
00:15:13,099 --> 00:15:14,099
Why?

167
00:15:15,929 --> 00:15:16,999
No reason.

168
00:15:18,299 --> 00:15:20,969
I just want to know
if they're better than me.

169
00:15:26,409 --> 00:15:28,309
But they're all the same.

170
00:15:31,479 --> 00:15:32,919
They're the same as me.

171
00:15:36,149 --> 00:15:38,889
Maybe it's hate against
the same kind of people.

172
00:15:57,369 --> 00:15:58,239
You know.

173
00:15:58,239 --> 00:15:59,239
Yeah?

174
00:15:59,779 --> 00:16:01,809
What if a post really does come up?

175
00:16:02,079 --> 00:16:03,109
About what?

176
00:16:03,349 --> 00:16:04,779
About Canada...

177
00:16:06,979 --> 00:16:08,349
My son?

178
00:16:11,219 --> 00:16:12,219
Yes.

179
00:16:13,789 --> 00:16:15,229
Will you admit it?

180
00:16:17,229 --> 00:16:19,329
I'll kill Writer Lee.

181
00:16:20,029 --> 00:16:21,329
Through you.

182
00:16:33,479 --> 00:16:34,809
I'll drive you home.

183
00:16:36,009 --> 00:16:37,009
Okay.

184
00:16:37,509 --> 00:16:38,719
Thanks.

