308
00:27:44,249 --> 00:27:45,919
Oh, and the two were best friends.

309
00:27:47,349 --> 00:27:48,319
Who?

310
00:27:48,819 --> 00:27:51,119
David and Bathsheba's husband.

311
00:27:57,389 --> 00:27:58,959
Things never change.

312
00:27:59,299 --> 00:28:01,029
May I take your order?

313
00:28:01,499 --> 00:28:02,529
