326
00:30:28,009 --> 00:30:29,309
I see.

327
00:30:32,309 --> 00:30:33,849
Did you drink a lot?

328
00:30:34,419 --> 00:30:35,749
No.

329
00:30:37,419 --> 00:30:39,489
