345
00:33:40,009 --> 00:33:41,299
Aren't you getting out?

346
00:33:43,089 --> 00:33:44,639
Oh, yes. I am.

347
00:33:56,919 --> 00:33:57,649
Oh!

348
00:33:57,649 --> 00:33:58,919
Dad.

349
00:33:58,919 --> 00:34:00,719
When did you get here?

350
00:34:00,719 --> 00:34:02,279
Right now...

351
00:34:02,279 --> 00:34:04,259
