361
00:35:45,689 --> 00:35:47,129
Lee Gang-jae.

362
00:35:49,359 --> 00:35:51,229
Amazing.

363
00:35:57,439 --> 00:35:58,939
He's a pro.

364
00:36:05,609 --> 00:36:06,379
<i>Yeah?</i>

365
00:36:06,379 --> 00:36:07,719
Oh, wow.

366
00:36:11,619 --> 00:36:13,659
Is this really Gang-jae's phone?

367
00:36:13,989 --> 00:36:16,019
I can't believe you picked up

368
