That's what's important.

534
00:49:09,829 --> 00:49:12,729
But they weren't really best friends.

535
00:49:12,729 --> 00:49:14,539
He was a subordinate.

536
00:49:15,499 --> 00:49:16,899
Saying it out loud,

537
00:49:17,969 --> 00:49:19,409
