723
01:01:28,139 --> 01:01:29,469
Lee Bu-jeong!

724
01:01:30,869 --> 01:01:32,409
Lee Bu-jeong!

725
01:01:33,269 --> 01:01:34,209
Yes?

726
01:01:34,479 --> 01:01:36,209
