730
01:02:16,549 --> 01:02:17,989
Sir, take a look at this.

731
01:02:28,129 --> 01:02:29,199
Sir!

732
01:02:30,129 --> 01:02:31,129
Huh?

733
01:02:31,499 --> 01:02:32,729
Is everything okay?

734
01:02:33,869 --> 01:02:34,799
What?

735
01:02:35,339 --> 01:02:36,259
Your apron...

736
01:02:39,839 --> 01:02:41,039
Oh. Jeez.

737
01:02:42,409 --> 01:02:43,439
Sir...

738
01:02:43,439 --> 01:02:44,439
Okay.

739
01:02:59,959 --> 01:03:01,999
The last time you came was...

740
01:03:03,429 --> 01:03:04,529
about a year ago.

741
01:03:04,529 --> 01:03:05,729
Yes.

742
01:03:05,729 --> 01:03:07,699
