743
01:03:07,699 --> 01:03:09,369
and you have no possibility
of being pregnant?

744
01:03:09,369 --> 01:03:10,799
Right.

745
01:03:11,039 --> 01:03:13,209
Change clothes and
go to the examination room.

746
01:03:13,209 --> 01:03:14,169
Okay.

