766
01:06:08,009 --> 01:06:08,919
<i>2nd.</i>

767
01:06:08,919 --> 01:06:10,519
<i>It's been a year today.</i>

768
01:06:10,519 --> 01:06:12,589
<i>Do you know what day it is today?</i>

769
01:06:14,959 --> 01:06:17,159
<i>Young man in the last unit
