<i>Yes.</i>

771
01:06:18,559 --> 01:06:20,829
<i>I think I've seen him before.</i>

772
01:06:21,259 --> 01:06:22,999
<i>The man who just left.</i>

773
01:06:24,459 --> 01:06:27,269
<i>What's wrong?
Did you forget your password?</i>

774
01:06:27,269 --> 01:06:30,299
<i>I put it in my vest and jacket.</i>

775
01:06:30,299 --> 01:06:32,739
<i>Shutting this down at this point</i>

776
01:06:32,739 --> 01:06:34,569
<i>is good for all of us, isn't it?</i>

777
01:06:35,179 --> 01:06:38,009
<i>Then go visit her with some snacks.</i>

778
